-5c0-3%200-3-1-2h-2c0-1-1-2-3-1-1%200-2%200-1-1v-3l-1-1'%20fill='%23d3d3d3'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e\" style=\"position: absolute;top:0;left:0;width: 100%;height:100%;object-fit: cover;object-position: center;\"><img src=\"/acorns/static/b2f80fe4585e440fb2fa079992e77a1f/c08c5/1593437565805.jpg\" data-vdom-skip=\"true\" data-vdom-cache=\"true\" alt=\"34岁女掌门摊上事！不走寻常路的美邦，要走哪条路？\" title=\"34岁女掌门摊上事！不走寻常路的美邦，要走哪条路？\" name=\"images/1593437565805.jpg\" data-src=\"./images/1593437565805.jpg\" class=\"front_image\" loading=\"lazy\" srcSet=\"/acorns/static/b2f80fe4585e440fb2fa079992e77a1f/e4a55/1593437565805.jpg 256w,\n/acorns/static/b2f80fe4585e440fb2fa079992e77a1f/36dd4/1593437565805.jpg 512w,\n/acorns/static/b2f80fe4585e440fb2fa079992e77a1f/c08c5/1593437565805.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-action=\"zoom\" style=\"max-width: 100%;position: absolute;top:0;left:0;width: 100%;height:100%;object-fit: cover;object-position: center;\"></div><br><div class=\"story_image_caption \">34岁女掌门摊上事！不走寻常路的美邦，要走哪条路？</div></div></div><p></p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">电视剧《一起来看流星雨》截图。</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">但美邦服饰最近一次引起人们注意，则是因为其34岁的女董事长胡佳佳被法院发了限制消费令。风光无限的美邦服饰董事长，怎么就突然不让坐飞机高铁等高消费了呢？</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\"><strong class=\"markdown_strong_asterisk\">一起房屋租赁纠纷令名门闺秀被“限消”</strong></p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">近日，上海市黄浦区人民法院对上海美特斯邦威服饰股份有限公司(简称“美邦服饰”)及公司法定代表人胡佳佳下发了(2019)沪0101执6212号限制消费令。</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">限制消费令显示，事情起源于美邦服饰与林华康、毛卫红的房屋租赁合同纠纷案。因美邦服饰未按执行通知书指定的期间履行生效法律文书确定的给付义务，法院依照相关规定，对美邦服饰采取限制消费措施，限制美邦服饰及胡佳佳不得实施相应高消费及非生活和工作必需的消费行为。</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\"></p><div class=\"story_image_container story_block_image\"><div class=\"story_image\"><div class=\"gatsby-wrapper-image\" style=\"display:inline-block;max-width: 100%;width:600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;position:relative;\"><div style=\"width:100%;display:block;padding-bottom: 185.15625000000003%;\"></div><img class=\"background_image\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='741'%20viewBox='0%200%20400%20741'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M184%2015h-1l-3%202-1%203%201%203c-1%203-1%203%201%202h4c1%200%202-1%202-3%200-3%201-4%202-2%202%201%202%202%201%203s1%203%203%202h5l1-7c1-1%200-1-2-2h-6v1c2%203%200%202-4-1l-3-1m-50%2094c-1%204-1%204%201%204%201-1%202-1%202%201h1c2-2%205-3%205-2%200%202%203%203%204%202h1c4%203%207-4%204-7h-5c-2-1-3%200-4%202s-1%202-2%201l-1-2-1-1-2-1-3%203m112%20528c-6%202-12%205-16%209l-3%202c-2%200-9%2012-11%2017l-3%205c-3%200-5%204-4%207l3%202-1-2c-1-3-1-3%201-4%202-2%203-1%202%202%200%203%202%205%203%204l1-7c0-21%2026-39%2048-33%2017%204%2029%2018%2030%2032l1%208-1%207c-4%2023-27%2037-49%2031-4%200-8-2-10-3-4-2-5-2-5-1l7%204c22%2010%2046%201%2057-21l3-12c0-4%201-6%203-6%201%201%202-5%202-7l-2-1c-3%200-4%200-4-2%200-4-6-15-11-20a43%2043%200%2000-41-11m5%2025c-4%201-11%207-11%209h-2c-5-3-10%202-7%206%201%202%203%203%204%202%203%200%203%200%204%204%201%206%202%207%204%205h3c2%200%202-1%203-3%201-3%202-3%207-3%207-1%208%200%208%203%200%202%201%202%203%202l5%201%201-2v-2c2%200%202-1%202-3%200-3%200-3%204-3l3-1-4-1c-3%200-3%200-5-3l-2-6-1-1c0-1-6-4-11-5-1-1-2-1-2%201%200%201%201%202%204%202%202%201%203%201%202%203%200%202%200%202%201%201%201-2%202-2%202-1l2%201%201%201-2%201-2%202c-1%202-4-2-3-4l-1-2c-2%200-2%202-1%204v2l-2-1c0-1-2-1-4%201l-4%201c-2%200-2%200-1-1s1-1-1-1l-3-1v-1l2-1%202%201%203%202v-3c-1%200-2-1-1-2%200-1%201-2%202-1l3-4-5%201m19%2033l-6%203c-1%200-2%202-1%203%201%202-4%204-9%203l-2-1%201-1%202-2c1-1%200-1-2-1-4%200-10-2-12-5-1-1-1-1-2%203%200%206%200%208%202%207l2%201c0%202%202%202%204%200h2c1%202%2014%202%2017%200h2c0%202%202%201%205-1s3-3%202-6c-1-6-1-6-5-3'%20fill='%23d3d3d3'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e\" style=\"position: absolute;top:0;left:0;width: 100%;height:100%;object-fit: cover;object-position: center;\"><img src=\"/acorns/static/20e21f1b07e9ca6cb9b9570d5e504b75/b4294/1593437565806.jpg\" data-vdom-skip=\"true\" data-vdom-cache=\"true\" alt=\"34岁女掌门摊上事！不走寻常路的美邦，要走哪条路？\" title=\"34岁女掌门摊上事！不走寻常路的美邦，要走哪条路？\" name=\"images/1593437565806.jpg\" data-src=\"./images/1593437565806.jpg\" class=\"front_image\" loading=\"lazy\" srcSet=\"/acorns/static/20e21f1b07e9ca6cb9b9570d5e504b75/e4a55/1593437565806.jpg 256w,\n/acorns/static/20e21f1b07e9ca6cb9b9570d5e504b75/36dd4/1593437565806.jpg 512w,\n/acorns/static/20e21f1b07e9ca6cb9b9570d5e504b75/b4294/1593437565806.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-action=\"zoom\" style=\"max-width: 100%;position: absolute;top:0;left:0;width: 100%;height:100%;object-fit: cover;object-position: center;\"></div><br><div class=\"story_image_caption \">34岁女掌门摊上事！不走寻常路的美邦，要走哪条路？</div></div></div><p></p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">上海市黄浦区人民法院下发的限制消费令。</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">据美邦服饰27日下午的回应，该公司及董事长胡佳佳的限制高消费令已解除，预计24小时后在相关执行信息网站上更新。</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">此次房屋租赁纠纷涉及到美邦服饰在上海市南京东路旗舰店的承租事宜。美邦服饰表示，此事在执行过程中，法院依照法律程序推进执行工作，公司也不存在有能力履行判决但拒不履行的情形。</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">“但因其中存在信息沟通不充分不及时的问题，产生了误解。由于该房屋历史原因，房屋具体坐落区域划分难以判断，导致迟迟无法履行返还义务。”美邦服饰解释。</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">6月29日，截至发稿时，中新网在中国执行信息公开网仍可查询到“案号：(2019)沪0101执6212号”的执行信息。</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\"></p><div class=\"story_image_container story_block_image\"><div class=\"story_image\"><div class=\"gatsby-wrapper-image\" style=\"display:inline-block;max-width: 100%;width:640px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;position:relative;\"><div style=\"width:100%;display:block;padding-bottom: 52.34375%;\"></div><img class=\"background_image\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='210'%20viewBox='0%200%20400%20210'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M0%2037v37h401V0H0v37m194-21l-3%201h-4v10h4c3%200%203%200%203%203l2%202%201-2c0-2%201-3%203-3%203%200%204-1%204-5v-5h-3l-4-1-1-2-2%202m16%207v9h17V14h-17v9m30-7v12c-2%204-2%205%200%203l2-5c1-4%204-3%204%202%200%204%200%204%203%204l2-2h-1c-2%201-2%200-2-6%200-7%200-8-2-8l-2-1c-1-1-2-1-4%201m67-1c-3%200-3%201-3%205v5h14v-5c0-5%200-5-2-5h-9m43%201c3%200%203%206%200%206l-2%201%202%201c2%200%202%203-1%206-2%203%201%202%203%200l2-4c0-2%201-2%203-2%203%200%203%200%203%204%200%203%200%204%202%204l1-4c0-3%200-4%202-4l1-1-1-1c-3%200-3-6%200-6%201-1-3-1-7-1-5%200-9%200-8%201m22%208l1%208%201-1c0-2%204-5%204-3l2%201v-2c-2-2-2-3%200-6%200-2%200-2%201%201v4c0%202%200%202%201%201l2%201%201-5-1-4c0%202-2%203-2%201%200-3-4-2-4%200l-1-1c-2-3-2-1-1%203%201%202%200%203-1%205-1%201-1%201-1-5v-6h12v7l-1%208c-1%201-1%201%201%201s2%200%202-10l1-7h-17v9m-160-2c0%205%200%205%203%205%202%200%203-4%200-4v-1l2-1-2-2c-1-1%201-1%204-1%202%200%204%200%203%201l-2%202%202%201-1%201c-2%201-3%204-1%204l1-1c0-3%202-2%202%200%201%202-1%203-7%203h-4c1%202%2011%202%2012%201l1-8v-6h-13v6m-73-2c-1%202%200%2011%201%2012l1%201c0%202%204%206%206%206l1%201%203%201h11l2-1%202-2%201-2h1c0%201%203-1%203-3l1-1%201-1v-9c-2-3-3-2-3%204l-2%208-3%202c-1%203-3%203-2%200l-1-2c-2%201-2%200-1-1l-2-4c-4-1-8%201-8%203l-1%202v2c0%203-1%203-4-1-3-3-4-6-4-11%200-4-1-6-3-4M0%2092v8h194l200-1h7V84H0v8m7-2c-1%205%200%206%203%206%204%200%205-3%203-5-1-1-1-1%201-1l1%202c0%202%200%202%201%201l2%201%205%201h1c1%201%201%201%201-1l2-2c2%200%203%203%201%203v1l2-2c1-3%200-3-3-3l-4%202h-3l-1-1%201-1%201-1c-1-1-10-2-11-1H8l-1%201m77%2091v6l52%201h52v-11H84v4m2-2l-1%204v3h12l11-1h1a248%20248%200%200050%200l14%201h14v-4l-1-3-50-1-50%201'%20fill='%23d3d3d3'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e\" style=\"position: absolute;top:0;left:0;width: 100%;height:100%;object-fit: cover;object-position: center;\"><img src=\"/acorns/static/c651897c063c8f679356585e23c7cf9d/c08c5/1593437565822.jpg\" data-vdom-skip=\"true\" data-vdom-cache=\"true\" alt=\"34岁女掌门摊上事！不走寻常路的美邦，要走哪条路？\" title=\"34岁女掌门摊上事！不走寻常路的美邦，要走哪条路？\" name=\"images/1593437565822.jpg\" data-src=\"./images/1593437565822.jpg\" class=\"front_image\" loading=\"lazy\" srcSet=\"/acorns/static/c651897c063c8f679356585e23c7cf9d/e4a55/1593437565822.jpg 256w,\n/acorns/static/c651897c063c8f679356585e23c7cf9d/36dd4/1593437565822.jpg 512w,\n/acorns/static/c651897c063c8f679356585e23c7cf9d/c08c5/1593437565822.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-action=\"zoom\" style=\"max-width: 100%;position: absolute;top:0;left:0;width: 100%;height:100%;object-fit: cover;object-position: center;\"></div><br><div class=\"story_image_caption \">34岁女掌门摊上事！不走寻常路的美邦，要走哪条路？</div></div></div><p></p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">截图自中国执行信息公开网</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\"><strong class=\"markdown_strong_asterisk\">父亲是<strong class=\"markdown_strong_asterisk\"><strong class=\"markdown_strong_asterisk\">曾</strong></strong>蝉联3年中国服装界首富的周成建</strong></p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">此事一出，相比于房屋租赁纠纷本身，大家更关心的还是此次事件的主人公胡佳佳。</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">1986年出生的胡佳佳为美邦服饰创始人周成建之女，现任美邦服饰法定代表人、董事长。周成建则是曾连续3年蝉联中国服装行业首富的传奇人物。</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">美邦服饰创立于1995年，拥有“Metersbonwe”和“ME&amp;CITY”两大品牌，2008年在深交所上市，因宣传语“不走寻常路”和众多“流量明星”的代言，旗下美特斯邦威品牌一度风靡全国。</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">花儿乐队、郭富城、周杰伦、张韶涵、潘玮柏、林志玲、李易峰等一众明星，都曾经是美特斯邦威的品牌代言人。哪个80、90后，没有在美特斯邦威的镜子前挑选衣服的记忆呢？</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">《胡润服装富豪榜》显示，周成建身家从2008年的160亿元一路上涨至2010年的216亿元，周成建也曾在当年的福布斯中国富豪榜中排名第16名。到2011年底，美邦市值达到261亿元，是当时品牌服装板块第一大市值公司。</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\"></p><div class=\"story_image_container story_block_image\"><div class=\"story_image\"><div class=\"gatsby-wrapper-image\" style=\"display:inline-block;max-width: 100%;width:640px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;position:relative;\"><div style=\"width:100%;disp